data: {"type":"text_delta","delta":"I’ve got the core site facts: The Star Brisbane location, all-day dining hours, bookings through SevenRooms, menus/banquets/functions/drinks, the fire-and-lamb positioning, 120-seat dining room, private 10-seater, and 140-bottle wine list. I’m pulling the styling layer now so the concept inherits the actual dark, charred Mediterranean brand rather than a generic restaurant look."}

