id: 34
event: agent
data: {"type":"text_delta","delta":"Brand system: near-black charcoal base, white logo/navigation, hard uppercase headings, thin black hairlines, restrained ember red from the source CSS, and photography-led sections with square/portrait crop rhythm. I’m codifying that into `brand-spec.md`, then I’ll build `index.html` plus local image assets."}

