flavour.</h1>\n275:            <a class=\"btn btn-primary\" href=\"https://www.sevenrooms.com/explore/darkshepherd/reservations/create/search?venues=darkshepherd,pompetteau,yamasgreekdrink,stilts,richandrarerestaurant,fatcowrestaurant,longwangchopstickhouse,opabarmezze,massimorestaurantandbar,foshbarrestaurant\">Reserve a table</a>\n280:          <img src=\"assets/dining-room.jpg\" alt=\"Dark Shepherd dining room\" />\n286:    <section class=\"section\" id=\"menus\" data-od-id=\"menus\">\n291:            <h2>Fire, flavour, and flair.</h2>\n332:    <section class=\"section\" data-od-id=\"signature\">\n336:          <h2>Lamb meets fire's embrace.</h2>\n350:          <img src=\"assets/slow-cooked-lamb.jpg\" alt=\"Slow cooked lamb at Dark Shepherd\" />\n356:    <section class=\"section\" id=\"functions\" data-od-id=\"functions\">\n359:          <img src=\"assets/service-room.jpg\" alt=\"Dark Shepherd hospitality and dining service\" />\n364:          <h2>A rite of passage, not a room hire.</h2>\n374:    <section class=\"section\" data-od-id=\"quote\">\n382:    <section class=\"section\" id=\"visit\" data-od-id=\"visit\">\n387:            <h2>Find us at The Terrace.</h2>\n389:          <a class=\"btn btn-primary\" href=\"https://www.sevenrooms.com/explore/darkshepherd/reservations/create/search?venues=darkshepherd,pompetteau,yamasgreekdrink,stilts,richandrarerestaurant,fatcowrestaurant,longwangchopstickhouse,opabarmezze,massimorestaurantandbar,foshbarrestaurant\">Book now</a>\n","isError":false}

